sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Customer
    participant System as Car Rental System
    participant Payment as VNPAY
    actor Operator
    actor Staff
    actor Driver

    Customer->>System: Select vehicle, rental dates, submit booking request
    System-->>Customer: Create booking (PENDING) and request payment

    Customer->>Payment: Complete payment
    Payment-->>System: Return payment result

    alt Payment successful
        System-->>Customer: Booking confirmed (CONFIRMED)
        Operator->>System: Assign staff/driver
        System-->>Operator: Booking moves to ASSIGNED

        Staff->>System: Perform vehicle handover (pickup inspection)
        System-->>Staff: Booking moves to IN_PROGRESS

        alt With driver
            Driver->>System: Accept trip
            Driver->>System: Start trip
            Driver->>System: Complete trip
            System-->>Driver: Booking COMPLETED
        else Self-drive
            Staff->>System: Perform vehicle return inspection
            System-->>Staff: Booking COMPLETED
        end

        System-->>Customer: Notify booking completion
    else Payment failed or expired
        System-->>Customer: Booking cancelled (CANCELLED)
    end
